  id: Ghost Ship
  displayName: Ghost Ship
  introText: An abandoned vessel phases in and out of reality in front of you, circling
    your ship.
  choices:
  - choiceText: Attempt to board the ship
    outcomeText: As you board the ship it becomes stable in reality again, but is
      completely empty...
